Ariona is a wise and kind soul, almost too kind; 
he would not be safe in this accursed land
without protection.

When one loses the Soul, one loses the mind; 
a land barren of Souls is absorbed by fog
and banished to the infinite darkness.

You seem to have plenty about you. 
Surely you realize that you are a sacrifice; 
you are meant to die here.
